evidence.source_document: Notice of Voluntary Dismissal Without Prejudice
evidence.text: Plaintiffs Mayor and City Council of Baltimore and Economic Action Maryland Fund hereby give notice that the above-captioned action is voluntarily dismissed without prejudice against Defendants Consumer Financial Protection Bureau and Russell Vought.
MARGINAL ORDER APPROVING 50 Notice of Voluntary Dismissal filed by Economic Action Maryland Fund, Mayor and City Council of Baltimore.
